<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
   <meta charset="utf-8" />
   <link href="/static/css/w3css.css" rel="stylesheet">
   <!-- <link href="/static/css/mystyle.css" rel="stylesheet"> -->
   <link href="/static/css/prism.css" rel="stylesheet">

   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
   <meta name="theme-color" content="#919597">
   <title>Credential Verifier</title>



       <style>
        .logo-bar {
            padding: 1rem 1.875rem;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .logo-bar ul {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .logo-bar picture,
        .logo-bar img {
            height: 1.25rem;
            width: auto;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .logo-bar {
                padding-top: 1.875rem;
                padding-bottom: 1.875rem;
            }

            .logo-bar ul {
                column-gap: 1.875rem;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .logo-bar ul {
                column-gap: 2.5rem;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {

            .logo-bar picture,
            .logo-bar img {
                height: 1.875rem;
            }
        }
    </style>


</head>

<body>

       <div class="logo-bar">
        <ul>
            <li>
                <picture>
                    <img src="/static/images/nextgeneration.png"
                        alt="nextgeneration" width="220" height="53" loading="lazy" />
                </picture>
            </li>
            <li>
                <picture>
                    <img src="/static/images/gobierno.png"
                        alt="gobierno" width="308" height="53" loading="lazy" />
                </picture>
            </li>
            <li>
                <picture>
                    <img src="/static/images/plan.png"
                        alt="plan" width="161" height="53" loading="lazy" />
                </picture>
            </li>
            <li>
                <picture>
                    <img src="/static/images/cam.png"
                        alt="cam" width="190" height="59" loading="lazy" />
                </picture>
            </li>
            <li>
                <picture>
                    <img src="/static/images/alastria.png"
                        alt="alastria" width="282" height="59" loading="lazy" />
                </picture>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>


<div class="w3-half-centered">

   <div class="w3-content">
      <div class="w3-container w3-margin-bottom w3-center w3-border w3-large w3-verifier">
         <h2 class="">Credential Verifier</h2>
      </div>

      <p class="w3-large">
         This is the component that talks to the Wallet to receive the Verifiable Credential and hides the
         complexity from the application.
      </p>
      <p class="w3-large">
         The Verifier appears to the application as a normal Identity Provider like Google, Facebook, Microsoft,
         etc.
      </p>

      <div class="w3-panel w3-border">
         <div class="w3-cell-row">
            <div class="w3-container w3-cell w3-cell-bottom">

               <div class="w3-panel w3-card-2">
                  <h3>Identify with a certificate</h3>
                  <p>
                     If you have a certificate of representation, you can use it to login.
                     Please, click the button below.
                  </p>
                  <div class="w3-section">
                     <a href="cert/login?code={{ .authCode }}" class="w3-btn w3-black" title="Submit button">Login
                        with a certificate</a>
                  </div>
               </div>


            </div>
            <div class="w3-container w3-cell w3-cell-bottom">
               <div class="w3-panel w3-card-2">
                  <h3>Identify with a LEARCredential</h3>
                  <p>
                     If you are a LEAR you can use your LEARCredential to login.
                     Please, click the button below.
                  </p>
                  <div class="w3-section">
                     <a href="/wallet/login?code={{ .authCode }}" class="w3-btn w3-black" title="Submit button">Login with a VC</a>
                  </div>
               </div>


            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>

</div>
</body>

</html>